video.title: All American
video.synopsis: Culture clashes and brewing rivalries test a teen football player from South Los Angeles when he’s recruited to the Beverly Hills High School team.

episodes.synopsis: After accepting coach Billy Baker’s offer to play football for ritzy Beverly High, Crenshaw teen Spencer James struggles to fit in at his new school.
episodes.title: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: Spencer’s move to the Bakers’ home ruffles feathers, while his connection with Leila sparks envy. In Crenshaw, Coop falls in deeper with Shawn’s gang.
episodes.title: 99 Problems

episodes.synopsis: After questioning Spencer's loyalty to Beverly, Jordan gets a taste of Crenshaw. Coop must be honest with herself. Olivia and Leila try to reconcile.
episodes.title: i

episodes.synopsis: A crisis at a Beverly High party forces Spencer and Asher to bond. Coop turns to Shawn for help.
episodes.title: Lose Yourself

episodes.synopsis: A birthday present prompts Spencer to do some soul-searching. Jordan and Olivia make a surprising discovery.
episodes.title: All We Got

episodes.synopsis: Wary of her dad's new flame, Leila seeks Spencer’s help. Coop’s gang connections could jeopardize a community event. A rival taunts Billy.
episodes.title: The Choice is Yours

episodes.synopsis: At a tense homecoming dance, confessions threaten to ruin several relationships. Coop begins to fear Tyrone as Shawn attempts to turn a corner.
episodes.title: California Love

episodes.synopsis: Coop and Spencer urge Shawn to make a change. As a tragedy hangs over the homecoming game, Spencer and the team face some stiff competition.
episodes.title: Homecoming

episodes.synopsis: Spencer feels torn between his Crenshaw roots and his rising star at Beverly. Jordan stresses out about the drug test. Coop reels from recent events.
episodes.title: Keep Ya Head Up

episodes.synopsis: As Spencer plans an anti-violence rally in Crenshaw, Coop ignores his advice. Leila’s reputation is challenged. Billy learns that Jordan has a secret.
episodes.title: m.A.A.d. City

episodes.synopsis: Spencer is flustered when his old Crenshaw teammates show up at a college recruiting event. Olivia pays Asher a visit. Grace considers her own dreams.
episodes.title: All Eyez on Me

episodes.synopsis: As flashbacks reveal their struggles in the past, Olivia and Spencer each try not to revert to old habits. Coop’s father has a surprise.
episodes.title: Back in The Day

episodes.synopsis: Ahead of the playoffs, a midterm essay stumps Spencer while secrets about his father emerge. Jordan finds an unexpected ally.
episodes.title: Legacy

episodes.synopsis: The arrival of a figure from the past sparks heated confrontations. Coop makes a risky call. Leila urges Asher to self-reflect.
episodes.title: Regulate

episodes.synopsis: Revelations leave Spencer reeling and prompt Billy to make a painful confession. Coop tries to thwart a dangerous plan.
episodes.title: Best Kept Secret

episodes.synopsis: Tensions ride high for Spencer as Beverly High faces South Crenshaw for the championship game. Coop takes a final risk. Billy makes a tough decision.
episodes.title: Championships

episodes.synopsis: As his Beverly teammates celebrate their championship win, Spencer grapples with a decision. Corey confronts Grace. Billy does some soul-searching.
episodes.title: Hustle & Motivate

episodes.synopsis: Corey brings a surprising addition to the Crenshaw team. Jordan’s new attitude has disappointing consequences. Layla’s poised facade begins to crack.
episodes.title: Speak Ya Clout

episodes.synopsis: Spencer gives Corey an ultimatum. With newfound confidence, Coop participates in a rap battle. Billy finds his authority as coach being undermined.
episodes.title: Never No More

episodes.synopsis: Spencer’s growing concern for Layla has unintended effects. A high school reunion opens old wounds for Billy and Corey. Asher gets a visitor.
episodes.title: They Reminisce Over You

episodes.synopsis: After an intervention for Layla fails, she throws a birthday party for the Baker twins that goes awry. Spencer struggles to process Corey’s actions.
episodes.title: Bring the Pain

episodes.synopsis: Ahead of a tense exhibition rematch between Beverly and Crenshaw, Spencer and Darnell make a bet. Surprising news hands Jordan new responsibilities.
episodes.title: Hard Knock Life

episodes.synopsis: A trip to find Corey results in several poignant revelations. Meanwhile, the Bakers make their own discoveries while attending family therapy.
episodes.title: Coming Home

episodes.synopsis: A tragedy leaves Spencer numb to his football accomplishments. Jordan and Asher each receive unexpected information. Layla takes a big step.
episodes.title: Life Goes On

episodes.synopsis: Coop’s past catches up to her. As Spencer’s schedule fills up, Dillon resents him for being unavailable. An incident pushes Olivia to take action.
episodes.title: One of Them Nights

episodes.synopsis: Tyrone’s return has Spencer extra protective of Coop. Ahead of her cotillion, Olivia is angered by Asher’s priorities. Coop’s jealousy irks Patience.
episodes.title: Protect Ya Neck

episodes.synopsis: The community rallies around an injured Spencer. The threat of a gang war rises after Tyrone's actions. Jordan steps up for Billy.
episodes.title: Crossroads

episodes.synopsis: Eager to return to football, Spencer pushes himself beyond comfort. Coop’s guilt keeps her from moving on. Asher’s athletic progress raises concerns.
episodes.title: Only Time Will Tell

episodes.synopsis: Tyrone’s return puts Coop in defense mode. Spencer fights for a chance on the field. Asher’s secret weighs on Olivia. Laura pursues political ambitions.
episodes.title: The Art of Peer Pressure

episodes.synopsis: As Coop becomes a prime murder suspect, she resists help from Spencer, who is determined to protect her. Asher’s mistake puts Billy in a predicament.
episodes.title: Who Shot Ya

episodes.synopsis: Spencer goes overboard for another shot at recruitment. Asher struggles with guilt over the impact of his actions on Billy. Coop’s talent gets noticed.
episodes.title: Stakes is High

episodes.synopsis: As friends make summer plans, loneliness tests Olivia’s resolve. With South Crenshaw in danger, Spencer makes a dramatic decision – and so does Billy.
episodes.title: Decisions

episodes.synopsis: As summer ends, Spencer gives an interview that irks his old teammates. Billy’s new start hits a snag. A surprise awaits Coop when she returns from tour.
episodes.title: Season Pass

episodes.synopsis: Spencer deals with divided loyalties. Billy tries to earn his players’ trust. A new coach and her daughter catch Jordan, Olivia and Asher off-guard.
episodes.title: How to Survive in South Central

episodes.synopsis: Pressure builds for Spencer ahead of Crenshaw’s first game. A double date gone wrong brings summer secrets to the surface. Coop’s suspicions of Mo grow.
episodes.title: High Expectations

episodes.synopsis: Spencer begins therapy to unpack his trauma. Darnell receives sad news. Jordan’s focus falters as Simone second-guesses a crucial decision.
episodes.title: My Mind's Playing Tricks on Me

episodes.synopsis: After a painful realization, Spencer resists confronting Coop. Crenshaw’s losses weigh on Billy. Jordan suffers a blow. Olivia’s behavior raises flags.
episodes.title: Home Come

episodes.synopsis: Spencer heads to Cory’s cabin for some introspection, but when his friends arrive, an evening of carefree unwinding rapidly unravels into drama.
episodes.title: Teenage Love

episodes.synopsis: In a flashback to summer, the crew meets Coop on tour in Las Vegas, where one couple makes big plans and Spencer gains clarity on matters of the heart.
episodes.title: Roll the Dice

episodes.synopsis: Billy appeals to Principal Carter. Spencer and Coop each reflect on what homecoming court nominations mean. Tension builds between Layla and Olivia.
episodes.title: Canceled

episodes.synopsis: After a risky incident exposes a secret, Olivia acts in panic and Spencer must resist his instincts. Billy finds a surprising candidate for a new kicker.
episodes.title: Testify

episodes.synopsis: With the homecoming game ahead, Spencer hopes to keep a legacy alive. Jordan’s choices may have damaging consequences. Olivia seeks a new sponsor.
episodes.title: Put Up or Shut Up

episodes.synopsis: The police shooting of a young Black woman affects Olivia particularly deeply. A college scout shows interest in Spencer but has troubling demands.
episodes.title: The Bigger Picture

episodes.synopsis: Olivia’s recent podcast episode leaves Laura struggling with the fallout. Spencer asks his team to take action, which could bring consequences.
episodes.title: Fight the Power

episodes.synopsis: Spencer seeks Olivia’s help in throwing a graduation party for Grace. While attempting to organize a scrimmage game, Billy clashes with Carter once more.
episodes.title: Bring the Noise

episodes.synopsis: Spencer feels the heat in the lead-up to a high-stakes game. Coop’s upcoming 18th birthday evokes childhood memories. Laura faces an ultimatum.
episodes.title: Ready or Not

episodes.synopsis: When several unlikely duos each meet for an evening of fun, their hangouts have varied results, from unexpected camaraderie to disappointing conflict.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: A Friendsgiving dinner helps thaw some icy relationships. Spencer has second thoughts about his future, while Jordan and Asher seek to redeem theirs.
episodes.title: No Opp Left Behind

episodes.synopsis: Spencer, Jordan, Olivia and Simone visit an Atlanta HBCU, where experiences on campus give them an escape from the present and clarity for the future.
episodes.title: All American: Homecoming

episodes.synopsis: Jordan and Simone make an important decision. As Coop prepares for her tour, Preach breaks disappointing news. Grace’s new relationship shocks Spencer.
episodes.title: Int'l Players Anthem (I Choose You)

episodes.synopsis: The state championship approaches and Coop heads to Las Vegas, but new information and old enmities endanger relationships, futures — and even lives.
episodes.title: Surviving the Times
